name: 500 Flowers - 001
description:
Today it sprouts the newest and boldest project by Harmonic Flowers.

From now on, each new spin of Earth makes it sprout a brand new Harmonic Flower. So for the next 500 days, you can expect one of our "500 flowers" collection, each in its very own way.

So today we welcome to our garden the 001/500 flower. Curious for the next 499? Come visit our Harmonic Garden every new day!
